307
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:14,560
♪When the past emerges♪

308
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:19,960
♪Memories turn into a painting♪

309
00:14:21,680 --> 00:14:27,400
♪You're in it, and I love it♪

310
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:32,000
♪The past is like yesterday♪

311
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,440
- Silly girl.
- Tantan.

312
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,470
It's raining. Go back with me.

313
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:37,960
